	* gst-libs/gst/video/video.h:
	  Fix 32bit caps. Issue remaining: The macro names are chosen poorly.
	  They should probably be like
	  GST_VIDEO_PAD_TEMPLATE_CAPS_{RGB,BGR,RGBx,BGRx}.

