	(gst_videotestsrc_src_fixate):
	* sys/oss/gstosssink.c: (gst_osssink_sink_fixate):
	* sys/ximage/ximagesink.c: (gst_ximagesink_fixate):
	* sys/xvimage/xvimagesink.c: (gst_xvimagesink_fixate):

